    {
      "text": "A researcher is investigating the association between a new dietary supplement and the development of a rare type of cancer. The study includes 100 patients with the cancer and 100 healthy individuals. All of the following biases can occur in this type of study except?",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "A",
